==French==
===Verb===
'''savoir'''

# To [[know]] (something), in general
#:''Il est difficile à '''savoir''' si elle ment''
#::''It's difficult to know if she's lying''
# [[can]], to know how to

====Usage====
:Use [[connaître]] if you want to say you know someone

====Synonyms====
*[[être capable de]]

===Related terms===
*[[savoir-faire]]
*[[savoir-vivre]]

